title: Stieg Larsson's Millennium Trilogy English Dubbed
description:
Source: R1 Blu-Ray

I had a heck of a time finding these with English audio so went out and bought a Blu-Ray drive for the pc and ripped my copies for back-up. I am limited on upload speed so it may take a little time to get some seeders going but I will seed till there are 6 more seeders.

-------------------------------------------------------
Designed for direct playback on Apple TV, iPad, iPhone & iPod Touch 4th gen, PS3, WDTV, Xbox360, Popcorn Hour, VLC.
